{"surah": 112, "verses": [{"id": 1, "text": "قُلْ هُوَ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>للَّهُ أَحَ<tajweed class=qalaqah>د</tajweed>ٌ <span class=end>١</span>"}, {"id": 2, "text": "ٱللَّهُ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed><tajweed class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</tajweed>صَّمَ<tajweed class=qalaqah>د</tajweed>ُ <span class=end>٢</span>"}, {"id": 3, "text": "لَمْ يَلِ<tajweed class=qalaqah>دْ</tajweed> وَلَمْ يُولَ<tajweed class=qalaqah>دْ</tajweed> <span class=end>٣</span>"}, {"id": 4, "text": "وَلَمْ يَك<tajweed class=idgham_wo_ghunnah>ُن ل</tajweed>َّهُ<tajweed class=madda_normal>ۥ</tajweed> كُفُوًا أَحَ<tajweed class=qalaqah>د</tajweed>ُۢ <span class=end>٤</span>"}]}